{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/flexbox-centering/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"CSS para impacientes"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9aa44dbf-9a96-58ba-aee9-bbf1067a378d","excerpt":"Horizontally and vertically centers a child element within a parent element using . Explanation  enables flexbox.  centers the child horizontally.  centers the…","html":"<p>Horizontally and vertically centers a child element within a parent element using <code class=\"language-text\">flexbox</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>flexbox-centering<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Centered content.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.flexbox-centering</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">justify-content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">align-items</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4>Explanation</h4>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">display: flex</code> enables flexbox.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">justify-content: center</code> centers the child horizontally.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">align-items: center</code> centers the child vertically.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Browser support</h4>\n<p><span class=\"snippet__support-note\">⚠️ Needs prefixes for full support.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#feat=flexbox\">https://caniuse.com/#feat=flexbox</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Flexbox centering","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/flexbox-centering/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/focus-within/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Focus Within"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fit-image-in-container/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Fit image in container"}}}}}